Class GnAlbum

java.lang.Object
  com.gracenote.gnsdk.GnObject
      com.gracenote.gnsdk.GnDataObject
          com.gracenote.gnsdk.GnAlbum

public class GnAlbum
extends GnDataObject

Collection of audio recordings. Provides access to album cover art when received from a query object with content enabled in lookup data.
